# Input
```css
/* should generate diagnostics */

/* allowProperties: only accent-color is allowed, backdrop-filter is still flagged */
a { accent-color: red; backdrop-filter: blur(10px); }

/* allowSelectors: only "has" is allowed, fullscreen is still flagged */
h1:has(+ h2) { margin: 0; }
h1:fullscreen { color: red; }

/* allowFunctions: only color-mix is allowed, abs is still flagged */
a { width: abs(20% - 100px); }

/* allowMediaConditions: only scripting is allowed, inverted-colors is still flagged */
@media (inverted-colors: inverted) { a { color: red; } }

/* allowPropertyValues: only clip-path:fill-box is allowed, stroke-box is still flagged */
a { clip-path: stroke-box; }

```

